Move Object

Moves an object to a new location.

public

Parameters:
string $source_bucket (Required) The name of the bucket that contains the source file.
string $source_filename (Required) The source filename that you want to copy.
string $dest_bucket (Required) The name of the bucket that you want to copy the file to.
string $dest_filename (Required) The filename that you want to give to the copy.
string $acl - (Optional) One of the following options: S3_ACL_PRIVATE, S3_ACL_PUBLIC, S3_ACL_OPEN, or S3_ACL_AUTH_READ. Defaults to S3_ACL_PRIVATE.
